short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Collaborate with anyone, anywhere using Meet Extension
short.zh_CN: 使用会议功能所必须的扩展程序，帮助您随时随地与所有人协同工作。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: IWS is the collaboration companion that works the way teams do: flexibly and simply, in real-time or anytime. With the IWS Meet Extension for Google Chrome, users are able to collaborate with anyone, anywhere, and on any device. Keeping everyone connected and up to date helps teams never miss a beat. The Meet extension allows Chrome Users to host or join Video and Voice conferences, screen share anything on your desktop, live share any documents and remote control another desktop. It lets members white-board as well as easily annotate files. Also, the entire meeting can be recorded and stored for later use.
long.zh_CN: IWS是一款功能强大的协作类应用,个人和团队用户能够基于分享的内容实时的进行沟通和协作。用户可以进行聊天，会议，屏幕共享，页面标注，上传和导入文件以及创建可视化的声音和视频，所有这一切都只需要一个应用。从IWS通讯录里找到同事开始你的会话，一切轻松完成。
